[[2026-04-15 15:31:20]] {CREATE #1: Create environment config schema and CLI | Environment config dataclass (name, member, document_root, stages, scope, objectives, model config, corrections paths). CLI: create, list, show, delete. JSON files in environments/ directory. }
[[2026-04-15 15:31:23]] {CREATE #2: Create pipeline runner with stage orchestration | PipelineRunner that chains all 9 stages (extract→profile→parse→resolve→taxonomy→standards→graph→vectorstore→eval). Configurable --start/--end by name or number. Each stage returns StageResult with stats/timing/errors. Supports environment configs and standalone mode. }
