[[2026-04-15 15:31:30]] {CREATE #5: Add error code catalog to all pipeline modules | Module-prefixed error codes (EXT-001, PRF-001, PRS-001, etc.) with structured error reporting. Each module gets an error code enum and raises/logs with codes. }
